lead_paragraph: Sweden have included Hamburg midfielder Albin Ekdal in their 23-man squad for Euro 2016, despite the fact the 26-year-old is still recovering from a deep wound in his back.

headline.print_headline: Sweden Include Wounded Ekdal in Euro 2016 Squad
